rows.name: Did you get the Buoyweed for me?

rows.label: qst000402_msg0002
rows.name: Thanks so much! Now I can practice!

rows.label: qst000402_msg0003
rows.name:
If I tie this to myself, my body
will float and I'll be safe!

rows.label: qst000402_msg0004
rows.name:
Then I won't have to worry about
putting my face in the water, and
after that, it'll be a piece of cake!

rows.label: qst000402_msg0005
rows.name: I'll be able to swim in no time!

rows.label: qst000402_msg0006
rows.name:
Here's a little something
for you. Thanks again!
